summary: Mila Selaayn is a dark elf thief follower wielding an ebony bow and donning thieves guiled apparel. UNP body type
descriptionHtml:
[center][b][i]Mila Selaayn [/i][/b]





[b][u]Information[/u]:[/b]

[b]Location[/b]: New Gnisis Cornerclub - Windhelm
[b]Body Type[/b]: UNP
[b]Race[/b]: Dark Elf
[b]Weight[/b]: 1.00
[b]Height[/b]: 1.00
[b]Voice[/b]: FemaleSultry
[b]Marriable[/b]: Yes
[b]Essential[/b]: Yes
[b]Weapon[/b]: Ebony Bow (Frost Enchantment)
[b]Armor[/b]: Thieves Guild Variant
[b]Level[/b]: Starts at Level 10, levels with you up to 80
[b]Additional Info[/b]: No crimes are off limits for Mila to perform, should you choose to make her commit any (but breaking the law is wrong you criminal >:(  )








-----------------









Screenshots are taken with Rudy ENB (with NLA)








-----------------









Compatible (and recommended) with [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/15524]AFT[/url]﻿
Mila SHOULD be compatible with RDO, but I haven't tested so please report any conflicts








-----------------









[b]Installation[/b]:
Install as you would any other follower mod, through mod manager or extract contents to your data folder (manual)








-----------------


[b]Thanks for downloading! This is my first mod so if anything should go wrong please report any problems to me and I'll try to get back to you right away![/b][/center]
